{"tid":2437749,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"致各位巴士迷、鐵路迷朋友","createTime":"2021-03-08T05:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T12:17:39.000Z","uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"049788f361f9d011f61cf50f0727f6729f131a55","tid":2437749,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"各位巴士迷、鐵路迷朋友：<br />\n<br />\n本人現在正式為去年12月發表巴士迷演說而道歉。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼現在才道歉呢？不是有人向本人施壓，亦不是現在才知錯。在這段時間，本人深刻反省錯誤。本人曾承諾不會做膠事，但當時萬萬不想到那影片很膠。本人深刻反省有關錯誤，是抹黑了巴士迷界，令人以為所有巴士迷都會做膠事。本人經兩個半月反省，為此深刻致歉。希望各位巴士迷可以原諒本人的愚蠢行為。本人會在巴士迷界相對低調，亦會放棄已收了的愛車，一切重新來過。<br />\n<br />\n巴鐵迷<br />\n羅哲琛 謹啟<br />\n2021.03.08<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd87566b1db3a0b0f5f4314c289183a39ee8bf5e","tid":2437749,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d677049b166284ea9f7c3d7144251a2c65eebfba","tid":2437749,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e491a596bbda9484c64c45e5f597f1fa2364120","tid":2437749,"uid":197782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:47:59.000Z","msg":"捉返自己出嚟bin係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0267278ae68bf1b804171c6ed8f9ed6b81d43673",